{
  "stem": "6195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "What's war about?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It's cheating your enemy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "That's how you can win.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Well, we got to the ghetto, only to be told to pick up the corpses that in the meantime were lying in the streets.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I've got the books with pictures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "How long were you in the ghetto for?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To 1943.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were taken-- first it was a [NON-ENGLISH] Arbeitslager, which is a compulsory work camp-- Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it was turned into a [NON-ENGLISH] Konzentrationslager, which didn't make much difference.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Amon Goeth.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After the war, they caught him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tried him in Cracow, and he was hanged in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of this I have a picture too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] An animal without any-- I mean, you can see reasonable animals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they shoot, they kill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this one was deriving some special pleasure out of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He could come out on a horse, having all of us lined up-- 20,000 of us-- and he will make a bet with another animal, like himself, that with one bullet he will kill 10 Jews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Line up one next-- after the other and shoot him-- shoot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Roll call.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And naked, just as you were born.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And stand in the snow or run in the snow for hours upon hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And once, I remember a young boy, because they counted us a few times a day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one was missing, a young boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He could have been 16, 17.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He tried to run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were standing there on-- in the snow, I think, a day and night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And next morning, they caught him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They brought him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They hung him.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
